query: SELECT p.id, p.address, p.price, pi.image_url, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY pi.image_url) as image_usage_count FROM properties p JOIN property_images pi ON p.id = pi.property_id WHERE pi.image_url IN (SELECT image_url FROM property_images GROUP BY image_url HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) > 1) ORDER BY pi.image_url, p.id;
